channel.title: Jonny Nothing - Nothing But Net [Album]
channel.description: Hey folks, been using Auxy for a few months and have produced over 100 tracks just this year and am having a blast cultivating this new talent I didn't know I had. I did not consider myself a musician prior to discovering Auxy but I'm really in awe at the power of this app. My friends are dumbfounded how I'm creating so much music at this quality. This is my 6th concept album--I have been incredibly addicted to this app. I wrote this entirely in Auxy over about a week. https://soundcloud.com/prolerevolt/sets/nothing-but-net
